The [[Kollam|City Corporation of Kollam]] has a 55-member council headed by a [[Mayor]] assisted by a [[Deputy Mayor]].<ref>[http://www.kollamcorporation.gov.in/council Kollam Corporation Council]</ref> On an average, every ward consists of a population of around 7,000. Each ward is represented in the municipal council by an elected councilor. The Kerala Municipalities (KM) Act, 1994, governs all functions in KMC.<ref name="jnnurm.nic.in"/> Also there are 8 standing committees in the corporation for the ease of smooth governance of the city.<ref>[http://ksudp.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=166&Itemid=194 Committees in Kerala Corporations - Kollam]</ref> Each and every standing committee is headed by an elected councilor and he will become the chairman of the particular standing committee.<ref>[http://www.kollamcorporation.gov.in/standing-committee Kollam Corporation Standing Committees]</ref><ref>[http://www.hindu.com/2005/11/03/stories/2005110308360300.htm Standing panel chiefs elected]</ref> The standing committees are:
 
* Finance standing committee
* Development standing committee
* Welfare standing committee
* Health & Education standing committee
* Public works standing committee
* Town planning standing committee
* Tax appeal standing committee
* Education & Sports standing committee

==Zones==
[[File:Kollam City Map.png|right|thumb|Map of [[Kollam]] City]]
For the ease of administration, Kollam Municipal Corporation is divided into 7 zones.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ksudp.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=268&Itemid=70 |title=Building Permit Management System -Kollam Corporation |accessdate=16 December 2014}}</ref> There are zonal offices in each zones of the corporation.

* Central Zone – 1, Kollam City Corporation
* Central Zone – 2 (''Headquartered at [[Kollam Cantonment|Cantonment]]''), Kollam City Corporation
* [[Sakthikulangara]] Zone, Kollam City Corporation
* [[Vadakkevila]] Zone, Kollam City Corporation
* [[Kilikollur]] Zone, Kollam City Corporation
* [[Eravipuram]] Zone, Kollam City Corporation
* [[Thrikkadavoor]] Zone, Kollam City Corporation

==Councils==
Kollam city corporation consists of 55 divisions or councils spread across its 7 zones.

